ygData.msgSnippet: It is interesting how many EQ-ers I have seen that have moved over to the online Star Wars game.  I myself have not, but I know that at least half of my guild
ygData.messageBody:
It is interesting how many EQ-ers I have seen that have moved over to the online Star Wars game. I myself have not, but I know that at least half of my guild took some time from EQ to go play Star Wars, and have not returned yetΓÇª



-----Original Message-----
From: Luis Binnier [mailto:shannara200@...]
Sent: Friday, August 08, 2003 11:05 AM
To: theeverquesttavern@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [The EverQuest Tavern] Everquest and Star Wars



Hello All, I have been playing Everquest for about 2
1/2 years and I got the star wars one about a month
ago, I want to know if anyone else is playing star
wars also? I find the Star wars to be excellent theirs
more to it then everquest, but I still love everquest
and I play it also. I find I split my time between the
two of them, I want to know if any of you are doing
the star wars game on line and what you think of it

Peace to all

Luis
